README for ghdl-0.31-mcode-win32.zip 

This is the zip file installation of the GHDL 0.31 Windows mcode version.

See INSTALL for installation instructions.

See ./doc/ghdl.html for the GHDL user guide.


Program information from the ghdl --version command:

  GHDL 0.31 (20140108) [Dunoon edition] + ghdl-0.31-mcode-win32.patch
   Compiled with GNAT Version: GPL 2013 (20130314)
   mcode code generator
  Written by Tristan Gingold.
  
